<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>YelpCamp</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-0evHe/X+R7YkIZDRvuzKMRqM+OrBnVFBL6DOitfPri4tjfHxaWutUpFmBp4vmVor" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link href="/stylesheets/home.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
  <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
    <header class="mb-auto">
      <div>
        <h3 class="float-md-start mb-0">YelpCamp <span class="badge bg-success">EU</span></h3>
        <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-end">
          <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
          <% if (!currentUser) { %>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
          <% } else { %>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
          <% } %>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="px-3">
      <h1>Welcome to YelpCamp Europe!</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Jump right in and explore our many campgrounds. <br>
        Feel free to share some of your own and comment on others!
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-success fw-bold mx-1 mb-3" href="/campgrounds">Campgrounds</a>
      <a class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-danger fw-bold mx-1 mb-3" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseDisclaimer" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseDisclaimer">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path d="M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5zm.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z"/>
        </svg>
        Disclaimer
      </a>
      <div class="collapse opacity-75 my-3" id="collapseDisclaimer">
        * This project was based on some real data.
        Although, <mark>data may be irrelevant or out-dated</mark> (or incomplete).
        The main goal was to implement some features for learning purposes.
        Please, consider using another recourse if you are struggling to find a campground.
        <hr>
        Find more details at <a id="github-link" href="https://github.com/rawjrk/yelp-camp">Github repository</a>.
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
      <p>&copy; YelpCamp 2022</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-pprn3073KE6tl6bjs2QrFaJGz5/SUsLqktiwsUTF55Jfv3qYSDhgCecCxMW52nD2" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>